OL,3,CBritish aid worker killed in Ukraine
OL,4,Cdrone strike, according to NGO
OL,6,FThe family of a British aid worker
OL,7,Freportedly killed in a Russian drone
OL,8,Fstrike while volunteering in Ukraine
OL,9,Fhas been left in "limbo", an NGO has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FAnnie Lewis Marffy, 69, travelled from
OL,13,Fher home in Silverton, near Exeter,
OL,14,FDevon, in late May to deliver a green
OL,15,FToyota Rav4 packed with supplies.
OL,17,FShe arrived in Ukraine on 4 June but
OL,18,Fdid not meet co-ordinators from Aid
OL,19,FUkraine UK, the non-profit NGO which
OL,20,Fhad organised the mission, as planned.
