OL,6,FAfter a week of searching for Ms Lewis
OL,7,FMarffy, the organisation was contacted
OL,8,Fby the Kramatorsk district police
OL,9,Fdepartment with information that she
OL,10,Fhad been killed.
OL,12,FThe police report says that she
OL,13,Fsustained "injuries incompatible with
OL,14,Flife" after a Russian drone strike
OL,15,Fbetween 11 and 12 June, having parked
OL,16,Fthe Rav4 on a street in the contested
OL,17,FDonbas region.
