OL,6,FVladimir Putin is seeking full control
OL,7,Fover Ukraine's eastern regions of
OL,8,FDonetsk and Luhansk, which are known
OL,9,Ftogether as the Donbas.
OL,11,FRussia already controls almost all of
OL,12,Fthe Luhansk region, but Ukraine is
OL,13,Festimated to still hold onto around
OL,14,F30% of Donetsk.
OL,16,FThe area is of strategic importance to
OL,17,FUkraine, with strongly fortified
OL,18,Fcities like Sloviansk, Kramatorsk and
OL,19,FKostiantynivka acting as a barrier to
OL,20,FRussian forces.
