OL,6,FA police statement released says Ms
OL,7,FLewis Marffy's body "remains in an
OL,8,Farea of active hostilities, making it
OL,9,Fimpossible to conduct evacuation
OL,10,Fmeasures to transfer the body to the
OL,11,Fforensic medical examination
OL,12,Fdepartment".
OL,14,FHowever family have asked for a death
OL,15,Fcertificate to be issued, based on the
OL,16,FKramatorsk district police department
OL,17,Freport, either through local
OL,18,Fauthorities or the Foreign,
OL,19,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,20,F(FCDO).
