OL,6,FThey say this will allow them to
OL,7,Fgrieve properly and begin the probate
OL,8,Fprocess.
OL,10,FKatarzyna Bylok, founder of Aid
OL,11,FUkraine, told the PA news agency that
OL,12,Fthis process could take months or
OL,13,Fyears because of the lack of Ms Lewis
OL,14,FMarffy's remains.
OL,16,F"In a kill zone, where her remains
OL,17,Fare, it is impossible to recover them
OL,18,Fbecause whoever you send will also
OL,19,Fdie," she said.
