OL,6,FMs Bylok said there was an expedited
OL,7,Fprocess within Ukraine to certify
OL,8,Fdeaths where remains cannot be
OL,9,Frecovered, though this still takes six
OL,10,Fto 12 months.
OL,12,F"It leaves her family in a horrible
OL,13,Fred tape limbo," she added. "They will
OL,14,Fnever get her body. But what they need
OL,15,Fis the ability to close her affairs.
OL,16,FHer sons have their hands tied, they
OL,17,Fdon't have power of attorney."
OL,19,F"The procedures stating that you need
OL,20,Fto have remains or DNA for a death
OL,21,Fcertificate need to be updated."
