OL,6,FMs Lewis Marffy travelled through
OL,7,FEurope with a former soldier from
OL,8,FWales, who had to return to the UK
OL,9,Fafter becoming unwell in Poland.
OL,11,FShe was instructed to hand the vehicle
OL,12,Fover to Aid Ukraine teams in Lviv but
OL,13,Fdid not do so, instead insisting she
OL,14,Fwould continue to Kramatorsk, where
OL,15,Fthe vehicle was due to be delivered,
OL,16,Falone.
