OL,6,FAfter that, she was in sporadic
OL,7,Fcontact with co-ordinators from the
OL,8,Forganisation and ignored advice to
OL,9,Favoid frontline areas, leading them on
OL,10,Fa "wild goose chase" for the next week.
OL,12,FMs Bylok posted a picture of Ms Lewis
OL,13,FMarffy on Telegraph, asking for
OL,14,Finformation about her location, and
OL,15,Fwas contacted by police who said she
OL,16,Fhad been killed.
OL,18,F"She was very independent and when she
OL,19,Fturned her mind to do something, she
OL,20,Fdid it," she said.
