OL,6,F"She was very self assured and highly
OL,7,Fintelligent."
OL,9,FMs Lewis Marffy's son, Charlie Lewis
OL,10,FMarffy, told the BBC that the family
OL,11,Fwere not looking to blame anyone for
OL,12,Fwhat happened.
OL,14,FHe said his mother was in regular
OL,15,Fcontact with the family until 8 June,
OL,16,Fwhen communication stopped. "She was
OL,17,Fbrave, capable and determined, but we
OL,18,Fnever wanted her to go," Mr Lewis
OL,19,FMarffy added.
