OL,6,F"She was excited, happy to be doing
OL,7,Fsomething meaningful." He said the
OL,8,Ffamily had asked the FCDO and
OL,9,FUkrainian authorities for a death
OL,10,Fcertificate to be issued, based on the
OL,11,Fpolice report, and had been left
OL,12,F"dismayed".
OL,14,FPaying tribute to his mother, he
OL,15,Fdescribed her as "amazing, witty,
OL,16,Fkind, intelligent, adventurous"."She
OL,17,Fwas irreplaceable," Mr Lewis Marffy
OL,18,Ftold the BBC.
